{"tid":2366326,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"青年涉高呼「死黑警」被控 律師助取回手機片段證從未發生","createTime":"2021-01-14T11:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T13:27:10.000Z","uid":56115,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ca58fb28a42f2bacadb7a56458d30e73365f0d","tid":2366326,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:51:41.000Z","msg":"前年11月警方圍困理工大學抗爭者，校園外圍多處有抗爭行動。警方當日於尖東拘捕一名正在現場拍攝的青年，指他涉嫌高叫辱警語句，引起在場人士起哄，意圖激使他人破壞社會安寧，案件今日續審。<span class=\"red\">辯方早前播放被告當日所拍片段，力證被告並無如警員所指般大叫「死黑警」等語。</span>控方質疑片段的證物鏈完整性，惟辯方傳召負責自被告手機抄錄及複製片段的律師上庭作供後，法庭接納片段呈堂。控辯雙方將於下月5日結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n被告今決定不作自辯，只要求將片段呈堂。惟控方反對，指被告的手機雖被警方檢取，<span class=\"red\">惟被告不肯提供手機密碼，警方無法檢視手機內容，質疑片段的證物連貫性。</span>"},{"pid":"e1d8651aa870e78bf1a6f0c309a415cd1d9c2917","tid":2366326,"uid":56115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/6LZS57ABFNB7NE7WF5XBBDTVYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2F6LZS57ABFNB7NE7WF5XBBDTVYU%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVSiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=f893be96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2F6LZS57ABFNB7NE7WF5XBBDTVYU%2F&h=649638fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/6LZS57ABFNB7NE7WF5XBBDTVYU/</a>"},{"pid":"e18df4d7665e15d1271d6f4e6836be6974a25482","tid":2366326,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b75199bd42c9db4373ab8077e7b05071dbec32","tid":2366326,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e9